Maybe the server you’re running uses an interface that is not compatible with the MoparScape client. or if its a item your trying to spawn maybe its an item uncompatible with the MoparScape Client.

I havent used MoparScape client in a while, so i don’t know if they are nulls anymore… but in 3.2 there were a few
